      <title>德意志银行违规后，WeWork 基金失去最后一个伦敦办事处</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/wework-fund-loses-last-london-office-after-deutsche-bank-breach</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家与陷入困境的灵活办公巨头 WeWork Inc. 相关的基金在违反其银行契约后失去了对其最后剩余的伦敦财产的控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/wework-fund-loses-last-london-office-after-deutsche-bank-breach</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:46:55 GMT</pubDate>
