    <item>
      <title>由于电视前景恶化，派拉蒙债务被削减至垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</link>
      <description><![CDATA[标准普尔将派拉蒙全球公司的债务评级下调至垃圾级。普尔全球评级指出，由于该公司的广播和有线电视业务持续下滑，现金流面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/paramount-debt-is-cut-to-junk-on-deteriorating-outlook-for-tv</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:43:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Empower 首席执行官拒绝对 401(k) 计划的未来感到悲观</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-27/empower-ceo-rejects-gloom-over-future-of-401-k-plans</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Empower 首席执行官埃德·墨菲 (Ed Murphy) 告诉彭博社的凯蒂·格雷菲尔德 (Katie Greifeld)，批评者认为 401(k) 计划在刺激储蓄方面做得太少，这是错误的。他反驳了这样一种观点，即这些投资工具对于美国立法者来说是一个诱人的目标，他们希望通过终止该计划的税收优惠地位来寻求新的收入。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-27/empower-ceo-rejects-gloom-over-future-of-401-k-plans</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 17:41:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员等待沃勒言论，新兴市场货币下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/emerging-markets-fall-with-caution-on-us-inflation-yuan-policy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[大多数新兴市场货币周三走软，因为交易员在本季度末之前重新平衡了投资组合，并且市场等待美联储官员的言论。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-27/emerging-markets-fall-with-caution-on-us-inflation-yuan-policy</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 27 Mar 2024 10:57:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>标准普尔 500 指数在季度最后阶段攀升：市场总结</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[华尔街交易员在季度末推高股市，导致市场飙升近 10%，许多机构投资者可能会重新平衡其投资组合。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-26/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 26 Mar 2024 22:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
